dex.name: X, Y
dex.selection_rule:
(p.bankable or p.bankableish)
and (
    p.variantForm === null
    or p.variantForm?.name in ['Baby', 'Alternate', 'Gender', 'Therian']
)
and (
    p.specialForm === null
    or p.specialForm?.name in ['Mega']
)
and ba?.xy
dex.description:
The list of obtainable Pokémons in X and Y games.

We have the right to gender differences, to Pokémons with variable forms and transformations.
We also have the right to mega-evolutions!
dex.french_description:
La liste des pokémons obtenable dans les jeux X et Y.

On a le droit à des différences de genre, à des pokémons à formes variables et des transformations. 
On a aussi le droit aux méga-évolutions !
